# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a visiting american lawmaker criticized wednesday a pentagon ruling barring firms from anti-iraq war countries from bidding on reconstruction contracts .
# ::alignments
(c / criticize-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (l / legislate-01)
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "America"))
            :ARG0-of (v / visit-01))
      :ARG1 (r / rule-01
            :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Pentagon"))
            :ARG0-of (b / bar-01
                  :ARG1 (f / firm)
                  :ARG2 (b2 / bid-01
                        :ARG0 f
                        :ARG1 (c3 / contract
                              :mod (r2 / reconstruct-01)))))
      :time (w / wednesday))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok france rugby coach bernard laporte announced a ##-player squad on wednesday for their tour of argentina and new zealand .
# ::alignments
(a / announce-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Bernard"
                  :op2 "Kaporte")
            :ARG0-of (c / coach-01
                  :ARG1 (t / team
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "France"))
                  :ARG2 (s / sport)))
      :ARG1 (s2 / squad
            :consist-of (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (p3 / play-01)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (w / wednesday))
      :purpose (t2 / tour-01
            :ARG0 t
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (c2 / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Argentina"))
                  :op2 (z / zealand
                        :ARG1-of (n4 / new-01)))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok kellen winslow no longer will be known as a kansas city attorney and the analyst for radio broadcasts of missouri football games .
# ::alignments

      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Kkellen"
                  :op2 " winslow"))
      :ARG2 (a / and
            :op1 (a2 / attorney
                  :mod (c / city
                        :location (s / state
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Arkansas"))))
            :op2 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (a3 / analyze-01
                        :ARG1 (b / broadcast-01
                              :ARG1 (g / game
                                    :mod (f / football)
                                    :mod (t / team
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Missouri")))
                              :medium (r / radio)))))
      :time (n4 / no-longer))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :name (n / name

                        :op2 "Britain")))

            :ARG2 (u / under

            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday))
            :location (h / hill
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Shinnecock")))
      :ARG1-of (a / advertise-01))

                        :poss (n3 / nation))
                  :ARG1-of (f / fear-01
                        :ARG0 (m4 / many)))))

            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "Bethlehem")

                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Bible")))
      :accompanier (c4 / call-03
            :ARG1 (p / pump-01
                  :ARG0 (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                              :ARG1 (b2 / business))
                        :mod (ii2 / international))
                  :ARG1 (m / money)
                  :ARG2 (e / economy
                        :ARG0-of (s2 / struggle-02)))
            :ARG2 p2))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Zhu"
                  :op2 "Rongji")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "China"))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / premier
                        :mod (v / vice))))
      :ARG1 (h2 / hope-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (f / fruitful
                  :time (f2 / future)
                  :ARG2-of (h3 / have-degree-91
                        :ARG1 (c2 / cooperate-01
                              :ARG0 c
                              :ARG1 (c3 / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Zimbabwe"))
                              :ARG1-of (f3 / friendly-01))
                        :ARG3 (m / more))))
      :ARG2 (p3 / person
            :name (n4 / name
                  :op1 "Simon"
                  :op2 "Muzenda")
            :ARG0-of (v2 / visit-01)
            :ARG0-of (h4 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 c3
                  :ARG2 (p4 / president
                        :mod (v3 / vice))))
      :time (t2 / today))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok war 's refugees pushed toward the pakistani frontier by the thousands friday , fleeing a bombarded southern afghan city to scramble toward sanctuary .
# ::alignments
(p / push-01
      :ARG0 (r / refugee
            :poss (w / war)
            :ARG0-of (f / flee-05
                  :ARG1 (c / city
                        :location (s / south)
                        :location (c2 / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Afghanistan"))
                        :ARG1-of (b / bomb-01))
                  :purpose (s2 / scramble-01
                        :ARG0 r
                        :destination (s3 / sanctuary))))
      :ARG1 r
      :ARG2 (f2 / frontier
            :mod c2)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f3 / friday))
      :quant (m / multiple
            :op1 1000))

# ::id 8 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok barack obama urged world powers tuesday to agree a strategy to kickstart the global economy at next week 's g## summit as stocks soared on the back of the us president 's new plan to mop up toxic debt .
# ::alignments
(u / urge-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Barack"
                  :op2 "Obama"))
      :ARG1 (p2 / power
            :mod (w / world))
      :ARG2 (a / agree-01
            :ARG0 p2
            :ARG1 (s / strategy
                  :purpose (s2 / start-01
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (e / economy
                              :mod (g / globe))
                        :time (s3 / summit
                              :mod (g2 / g##)
                              :time (w2 / week
                                    :mod (n2 / next))))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday))
      :time (s4 / soar-01
            :ARG1 (s5 / stock)
            :location (b / back
                  :part-of (p3 / plan-01
                        :ARG0 (p4 / person
                              :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 (c / country
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "United"
                                                :op2 "States"))
                                    :ARG2 (p5 / president)))
                        :ARG1 (m / mop-up-02
                              :ARG0 p4
                              :ARG1 (d2 / debt
                                    :mod (t2 / toxic)))
                        :ARG1-of (n4 / new-01)))))

# ::id 9 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok two u.s. soldiers were killed and four others wounded by roadside bomb attacks in the iraqi capital on tuesday , the u.s. military said on wednesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (m / military
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "U.S.")))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (k / kill-01
                  :ARG0 (a2 / attack-01
                        :ARG1 (s2 / side
                              :part-of (r / road))
                        :instrument (b / bomb)
                        :location (c2 / city
                              :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 c
                                    :ARG2 (c3 / capital)))
                        :time (d / date-entity
                              :weekday (t / tuesday)))
                  :ARG1 (s3 / soldier
                        :quant 2
                        :mod c))
            :op2 (w / wound-01
                  :ARG0 a2
                  :ARG1 s3
                  :quant 4
                  :mod c))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (w2 / wednesday)))

                                    :mod (m2 / machine)

            :weekday (m3 / monday)))

            :ARG0 y
            :ARG1 (w / wave-04
                  :ARG1 (r2 / refinancing)
                  :mod (l / last))))

# ::id 1946 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok have you ever played that halloween game where you 're blindfolded and told to stick your hands in bowls that contain eyeballs -lrb- peeled grapes -rrb- , tongues -lrb- pickles -rrb- and teeth -lrb- uncooked popcorn -rrb- ? it might not be convincing , but the idea -- being close to things that were once inside a person -- is downright creepy .

                        :ARG2 h)))
      :time (e2 / ever)
      :snt2 (h3 / have-concession-91

                        :ARG0 (ii / idea
